name: NMOS
body:
# NMOS
An OS I'm working on.

## Compiling ##

### All files: ###

	make
	
or
	make all

### Specific file: ###
	make foo.c
	
Replace foo.c with the name of the file.

### Make and run: ###
	make run
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
